### =============================================
### Kafka Connect REST API
### Base URL: http://localhost:8083
### =============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8083

### =============================================
### HEALTH & INFO
### =============================================

### Get Kafka Connect cluster info
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### Get list of connector plugins
GET {{baseUrl}}/connector-plugins

###

### =============================================
### LIST CONNECTORS
### =============================================

### List all connectors
GET {{baseUrl}}/connectors

###

### List all connectors with status
GET {{baseUrl}}/connectors?expand=status

###

### List all connectors with info
GET {{baseUrl}}/connectors?expand=info

###

### =============================================
### TEAMS CONNECTOR
### =============================================

### Create teams source connector
POST {{baseUrl}}/connectors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "sqlserver-teams-source-connector",
  "config": {
    "connector.class": "io.debezium.connector.sqlserver.SqlServerConnector",
    "tasks.max": "1",
    "database.hostname": "host.docker.internal",
    "database.port": "1433",
    "database.user": "debezium_user",
    "database.password": "Debezium@2025!",
    "database.names": "sport",
    "database.encrypt": "false",
    "topic.prefix": "cdc",
    "table.include.list": "dbo.teams",
    "schema.history.internal.kafka.bootstrap.servers": "kafka:29092",
    "schema.history.internal.kafka.topic": "schema-changes.sport",
    "database.history.kafka.bootstrap.servers": "kafka:29092",
    "database.history.kafka.topic": "dbhistory.sport.teams",
    "key.converter": "org.apache.kafka.connect.json.JsonConverter",
    "key.converter.schemas.enable": "true",
    "value.converter": "org.apache.kafka.connect.json.JsonConverter",
    "value.converter.schemas.enable": "true",
    "include.schema.changes": "true",
    "snapshot.mode": "initial"
  }
}

###

### Get teams connector status
GET {{baseUrl}}/connectors/sqlserver-teams-source-connector/status

###

### Get teams connector config
GET {{baseUrl}}/connectors/sqlserver-teams-source-connector/config

###

### Pause teams connector
PUT {{baseUrl}}/connectors/sqlserver-teams-source-connector/pause

###

### Resume teams connector
PUT {{baseUrl}}/connectors/sqlserver-teams-source-connector/resume

###

### Restart teams connector
POST {{baseUrl}}/connectors/sqlserver-teams-source-connector/restart

###

### Delete teams connector
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/connectors/sqlserver-teams-source-connector

###

